GP MASTERY PROGRAMME

**Phase 1: IGNITE**

*The Complete 12-Lesson Arc*

| **Phase Duration** | 12 weeks (3 months) — 1 session per week, 2 hours each |
| --- | --- |
| **Target Progression** | Level 0–1 → Level 2–3 (U/S/E/D → C/B range) |
| **3 Sub-Phases** | Month 1: ARGUE Toolkit (L1–4) → Month 2: Theme Deep-Dives (L5–8) → Month 3: Exam Sharpening (L9–12) |
| **Progress Data Points** | 5 formal checkpoints: L1 (intro), L4 (first essay), L8 (boss battle essay), L11 (first AQ), L12 (full exam sim) |

